## VMKeyboard.up() method

Sends a low-level keyup event to the virtual machine.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
up(key: string): Promise<void>;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  key | string | Name of the key (cf [Key](./vm-providers.key.md)<!-- -->) or its corresponding character, for example <code>PageUp</code> or <code>a</code>. |
